          "Name of LNG carrier, with a preference given to the most common name available in an IMO number lookup. Note if the ship is not yet named, and is only identified by a hull number without more specific characteristics, we add an abbreviated name of the shipyard in parentheses to distinguish any hull numbers that might be duplicated across shipyards. This ensures that all carrier names are unique in the data set. Note also that if a ship has not been formally named yet, we do not consider it active. Alternatively, if a naming ceremony has occurred, we consider construction complete and mark the carrier active unless public evidence points to the contrary, e.g., for Arctic LNG 2 sanctioned ships built by Zvezda.",
